## Best Practices

### Responsive Design
- Use Tailwind's responsive prefixes (sm:, md:, lg:, xl:)
- Mobile-first approach
- Sidebar collapses below lg: breakpoint

### Dark Mode
- Use Tailwind's dark: prefix for dark mode styles
- Ensure sufficient contrast in both modes
- Test color combinations in both modes

### Accessibility
- Maintain WCAG 2.1 AA standards
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Ensure keyboard navigation works
- Provide aria-labels where needed

### Performance
- Use SVG icons where possible
- Optimize images
- Minimize shadow usage on mobile
- Use transition-properties judiciously